reviews.review_text: Scott Clugston This guys, Scott Clugston, is doing great things! I've heard things this year that I had back in the 90's but these new releases bring out everything hidden and burried in these analog tapes. I thought I was done building my digital dead collection but there is so much good stuff comming out right now and this guy and a few others are to thank. So this review is more for everything he has done this year. As for this show, I have not heard a better souding aud from the Wall of Sound tour.
